&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5 - &lt;span class="author-a-guz65ztxlz75zwz122zl6gz69zz71zz75zg"&gt;&lt;span id="result_box" class=""&gt;&lt;span class=""&gt;Panel: Debian - listening to experiences and contributing to the project&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It was held on february 3rd from 0am to 1am&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Speakers:&lt;/p&gt;
