&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://campuse.ro/events/campus-party-brasil-2018/talk/debian-ouvindo-experiencias-e-contribuindo-para-o-projeto-cpbr11"&gt;https://campuse.ro/events/campus-party-brasil-2018/talk/debian-ouvindo-experiencias-e-contribuindo-para-o-projeto-cpbr11&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
