&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://ftsl.websiteseguro.com/ftsl9/grade/detail.html?t=1505353768056&amp;amp;id=f426c77164f7052f97fdde247f54e2ea&amp;amp;type=1&amp;amp;pid=307&amp;amp;day=3"&gt;Description&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
